Package: tt-toplike-app
Source: tt-toplike
Version: 0.4.1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Tenstorrent <software@tenstorrent.com>
Installed-Size: 12266
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.39), libgcc-s1 (>= 4.2), tt-toplike
Recommends: libvulkan1 | libgl1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/tenstorrent/tt-toplike
Description: Native window host for tt-toplike (PTY terminal)
 tt-toplike-app opens a native graphical window (eframe/egui) that hosts
 tt-toplike-tui inside a PTY. The TUI runs as a child process; its VT output
 is parsed and rendered by a custom VT100 state machine so the full-colour,
 animated TUI visualizations appear in a proper desktop window.
 .
 Keyboard input is forwarded to the PTY child as ANSI escape sequences.
 The window resizes the PTY on geometry changes so the TUI always fills the
 available space.
 .
 Requires a graphical display (Wayland or X11) and Vulkan or OpenGL.
 Not suitable for headless / server installs.
